        </p>
        <p>
            I started to do online courses in CS for a few months. Eventually, I realized I really liked javascript and web development.
            I've spent the last 7 months working through full stack tutorials. I'm really proud of where I am now. I'm comfortable
            in the code. I'm comfortable problem sovling apps. I enjoy the feeling of seeing the hard work pay off in seeing
            a functional app come together.
        </p>
        <p>
